        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Make installs the primary plugin and skill usage signal",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- update the browse/detail/home UI to make installs the primary public usage signal for plugins and skills\n- add a visible \"Most installed\" plugin browse sort, including URL/search handling and client-side search-result ordering\n- swap public plugin and skill list metadata from download icons/counts to install icons/counts while keeping downloads available as an explicit sort\n- add package install metric dedupe storage and pruning so repeated installs from the same identity/day do not inflate package stats\n- add backend/API support for plugin `sort=installs`, including public API docs and client package API coverage\n\n## Tests\n\n- `bunx convex codegen`\n- `bun run test convex/downloadMetrics.test.ts convex/packages.stats.test.ts convex/packages.public.test.ts convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts src/__tests__/packages-route.test.tsx src/lib/packageApi.test.ts src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx src/components/SkillHeader.test.tsx`\n- `bun run ci:static`\n- `bun run ci:unit`\n- `bun run ci:types-build`\n- `bun run ci:packages`\n- `git diff --check`\n\n## Noted\n\n- `bun run ci:e2e-http` was attempted; the prod HTTP smoke passed, then the CLI GitHub repo dry-run fixture failed because `pwrdrvr/openclaw-codex-app-server` was not found.\n",
